{"tid":270603,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"將會係摩洛哥留兩個月左右，你問我答","createTime":"2017-06-04T12:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T02:35:29.000Z","uid":32932,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6559aa997a3ad120255887c3a1d617d02a199c4b","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"尋日係西班牙搭船去摩洛哥<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/202923_817de035fde2e531cd0638562dd458fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F202923_817de035fde2e531cd0638562dd458fc.jpg&h=50412ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好悶好眼訓<br />\n未兌錢未買sim card<br />\n隨時上唔到網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7842f932061cc7c37eea98a9289cca2b6c1f053c","tid":270603,"uid":54377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"去個邊咁耐有咩搞<br />\n我見你之前有個post話去歐洲打工換宿 最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去南法打工換宿"},{"pid":"7d0815a93fbc08d3e795cd07da4cb268cefa3e73","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教既人呢個月禁食緊<br />\n搞到我又要戇鳩鳩咁跟<br />\n佢地附近會有清真寺有announcement 同大家講可以開飯啦<br />\n大概7:30pm佢地先可以食野，announcement前係連飲水都唔得<br />\n機構有個男仔尋日一齊行national park，佢係咁係到講：I want to drink some fucking water, fucking water, fucking water<br />\n<br />\n呢個月佢地要做好事，例如share food，所以佢地習慣一班人坐埋一齊，自己帶d食物去同其他人分享<br />\n周圍d人都放滿食物，然後等announcement一到就開始鯨吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/203139_47eedc1a22974782330061aad272a04b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F203139_47eedc1a22974782330061aad272a04b.jpg&h=0c2efb3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/203149_e99b2d1701e315fc120109f2b278145a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F203149_e99b2d1701e315fc120109f2b278145a.jpg&h=e032d061&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/203229_4800f9888ec0dedd37495a4a2e7f6e13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F203229_4800f9888ec0dedd37495a4a2e7f6e13.jpg&h=46332a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多類似咖哩角、唔知咩酥嘅嘢"},{"pid":"ec1a2094d936f8beb17217981f7374aa36f6bb21","tid":270603,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:42:06.000Z","msg":"摩洛哥留邊？<br />\n係marrakech medina住過8日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d14af4e311f8241e8149e8e4fc2d86f9dd8442f","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去個邊咁耐有咩搞<br />\n我見你之前有個post話去歐洲打工換宿 最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去南法打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n去做義工啊<br />\n歐洲打工換宿收左皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身想join7月至8月 摩洛哥義工program<br />\n6月係歐洲打工換宿<br />\n但畀老母屌我唔洗搵工啊？<br />\n<br />\n於是我就join左6月至7月program<br />\n<br />\n好想冬天去冰島打工換宿"},{"pid":"6ba007530d01060430bd65fcbd64beefc7a2e583","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>摩洛哥留邊？<br />\n係marrakech medina住過8日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntangier 摩洛哥最北<br />\n天氣好好啊<br />\n廿幾度"},{"pid":"5affac9c35fda6f090809245cb4e37f2cc495bed","tid":270603,"uid":20416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去個邊咁耐有咩搞<br />\n我見你之前有個post話去歐洲打工換宿 最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去南法打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n去做義工啊<br />\n歐洲打工換宿收左皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身想join7月至8月 摩洛哥義工program<br />\n6月係歐洲打工換宿<br />\n但畀老母屌我唔洗搵工啊？<br />\n<br />\n於是我就join左6月至7月program<br />\n<br />\n好想冬天去冰島打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打工換宿同義工program 係邊搵？"},{"pid":"f54f392c7f5854517d79057f91ce96b5ed88059d","tid":270603,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:03:28.000Z","msg":"義工program 洗唔洗比錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07ac2d441814715ae568b8ad870b77db30fe7f0","tid":270603,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"日日食tajine 諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3002ae84a59dde491a8a3cedd42024f07005150","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"關於禁食，如果女仔黎m係唔需要禁食同埋唔需要祈禱 佢地可以正常食野 <br />\n不過呢段期間，就算佢地唔洗禁食都好，佢地都唔可以係街上面食<br />\n<br />\n因為禁食，公司都會調整員工既工作時間<br />\n我識一個摩洛哥女仔 佢返緊intern<br />\n本身係返8am至7pm<br />\n禁食期間係返9am至4pm"},{"pid":"bfcb6990dd695ef5a86ada45ad696c6b807072f3","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>義工program 洗唔洗比錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n經機構報<br />\n畀$2750 $1000可以拎返<br />\n包六星期食宿"},{"pid":"d97d87e1cb20b245778785ab9ac17275a75fa74b","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去個邊咁耐有咩搞<br />\n我見你之前有個post話去歐洲打工換宿 最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去南法打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n去做義工啊<br />\n歐洲打工換宿收左皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身想join7月至8月 摩洛哥義工program<br />\n6月係歐洲打工換宿<br />\n但畀老母屌我唔洗搵工啊？<br />\n<br />\n於是我就join左6月至7月program<br />\n<br />\n好想冬天去冰島打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打工換宿同義工program 係邊搵？</blockquote><br />\n打工換宿係一個叫helpx既網<br />\n義工program 係經AIESIC"},{"pid":"5d6020f070b7321e22531d25f4b583a09b0d5884","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日食tajine 諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173683161e30fd1c1cc46a7dea9bfcf0b3ecca21","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:50:10.000Z","msg":"今朝既早餐：<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/214621_233e4c2d574f98c8899accdd776428b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F214621_233e4c2d574f98c8899accdd776428b2.jpg&h=8b461bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/214650_8f8bc23285fd2f594986f836dc0ab78b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F214650_8f8bc23285fd2f594986f836dc0ab78b.jpg&h=28d8d9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我到底食緊啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話有芝麻、花生、花？、橄欖油（好似係）<br />\n佢話佢地禁食既時候，早餐就會食呢個<br />\n因為會畀到energy佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/214707_c6ebd0f57539623a81a7a52e81b7cbe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F214707_c6ebd0f57539623a81a7a52e81b7cbe1.jpg&h=aa717d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我估係摩洛哥薄荷茶 不過佢地加好多糖落去"},{"pid":"05e4e6408f6fcd2d81e67564f26e7e786f187013","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:26:41.000Z","msg":"好撚肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340326209f423e4c99d23d50d6cb731afd4606ae","tid":270603,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講日日食tajine真係會食到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7179d85a60890847bcd5e2815a2f04e172b2718e","tid":270603,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去個邊咁耐有咩搞<br />\n我見你之前有個post話去歐洲打工換宿 最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去南法打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n去做義工啊<br />\n歐洲打工換宿收左皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身想join7月至8月 摩洛哥義工program<br />\n6月係歐洲打工換宿<br />\n但畀老母屌我唔洗搵工啊？<br />\n<br />\n於是我就join左6月至7月program<br />\n<br />\n好想冬天去冰島打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打工換宿同義工program 係邊搵？</blockquote><br />\n打工換宿係一個叫helpx既網<br />\n義工program 係經AIESIC</blockquote><br />\n咁剩係比$2750就可以去咁遠？<br />\n使唔使interview?<br />\n除左摩洛哥仲有冇其他地方？<br />\n我都想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38cecfa1cb391c10d62103df6599909019b263c","tid":270603,"uid":89709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去個邊咁耐有咩搞<br />\n我見你之前有個post話去歐洲打工換宿 最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去南法打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n去做義工啊<br />\n歐洲打工換宿收左皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身想join7月至8月 摩洛哥義工program<br />\n6月係歐洲打工換宿<br />\n但畀老母屌我唔洗搵工啊？<br />\n<br />\n於是我就join左6月至7月program<br />\n<br />\n好想冬天去冰島打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打工換宿同義工program 係邊搵？</blockquote><br />\n打工換宿係一個叫helpx既網<br />\n義工program 係經AIESIC</blockquote><br />\n咁剩係比$2750就可以去咁遠？<br />\n使唔使interview?<br />\n除左摩洛哥仲有冇其他