係pizza hut食野<br />\n係餐廳返工都幾慘<br />\n係咁煮畀人食<br />\n但自己唔可以食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3616491a1597a9de62a973db8c9f8a51c1c7fed8","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>富二代</blockquote><br />\n富二代唔洗做義工啦<br />\n直接環遊世界啦"},{"pid":"4aea138423489c6804e979d57381483d416f6576","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今朝既早餐：<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/214621_233e4c2d574f98c8899accdd776428b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F214621_233e4c2d574f98c8899accdd776428b2.jpg&h=8b461bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/214650_8f8bc23285fd2f594986f836dc0ab78b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F214650_8f8bc23285fd2f594986f836dc0ab78b.jpg&h=28d8d9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我到底食緊啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話有芝麻、花生、花？、橄欖油（好似係）<br />\n佢話佢地禁食既時候，早餐就會食呢個<br />\n因為會畀到energy佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/214707_c6ebd0f57539623a81a7a52e81b7cbe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F214707_c6ebd0f57539623a81a7a52e81b7cbe1.jpg&h=aa717d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我估係摩洛哥薄荷茶 不過佢地加好多糖落去</blockquote><br />\n薄荷茶好出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係摩洛哥人都識沖 好多都會成棵薄荷隊落去浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係難飲 但都唔係好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb6aebdfb995d346df31d500cf985e240b5eeaf","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日日食tajine 諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTajine <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食左幾日食到怕</blockquote><br />\n未開始食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6be8015801ebb196fd7ea8c8e4b00568febc74d","tid":270603,"uid":90296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"巴打都係經aiesec?"},{"pid":"eede6f189979aba7f5a4e4f5fbb1d4759a9c1744","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:47:15.000Z","msg":"佢d supermarket好得意<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/014513_ddafbee2f7c8a369a2c7969d2f471bd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F014513_ddafbee2f7c8a369a2c7969d2f471bd6.jpg&h=fe9212da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/014546_5336018fa2f56e012b2b1b1796300512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F014546_5336018fa2f56e012b2b1b1796300512.jpg&h=110935db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/014605_4e623d3b43264d3d67baa79afca91651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F014605_4e623d3b43264d3d67baa79afca91651.jpg&h=fb5e1adf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/014623_85a965afdebeaa7e25bc60287c285a0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F014623_85a965afdebeaa7e25bc60287c285a0a.jpg&h=c1047e6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 我對唔住wtsapp 852 67006001條友<br />\n啱啱去supermarket<br />\n有條友抄我牌<br />\n佢話佢係東非唔知邊樹過黎<br />\n黎做intern<br />\n我唔想畀電話number佢 所以鳩打左個number畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1c062e6543caab97acf53b99966b0357660604","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打都係經aiesec?</blockquote><br />\nyesss"},{"pid":"ebfe70179029b6ef0f94fe50155cb7ec82622661","tid":270603,"uid":90296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打都係經aiesec?</blockquote><br />\nyesss</blockquote><br />\n聽日開始我都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過係Serbia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034e70935700c128d66b95a343dd3176e5a5b77f","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打都係經aiesec?</blockquote><br />\nyesss</blockquote><br />\n聽日開始我都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過係Serbia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我program聽日開始<br />\n你去serbia做咩？教英文？"},{"pid":"94ce670fe34774e75e1a59d0c22ccf258ab2665d","tid":270603,"uid":7731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去個邊咁耐有咩搞<br />\n我見你之前有個post話去歐洲打工換宿 最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去南法打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n去做義工啊<br />\n歐洲打工換宿收左皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身想join7月至8月 摩洛哥義工program<br />\n6月係歐洲打工換宿<br />\n但畀老母屌我唔洗搵工啊？<br />\n<br />\n於是我就join左6月至7月program<br />\n<br />\n好想冬天去冰島打工換宿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打工換宿同義工program 係邊搵？</blockquote><br />\n打工換宿係一個叫helpx既網<br />\n義工program 係經AIESIC</blockquote><br />\n咁剩係比$2750就可以去咁遠？<br />\n使唔使interview?<br />\n除左摩洛哥仲有冇其他地方？<br />\n我都想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有興趣知多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHi我係AIESEC global volunteer geh manager<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n咁基本上AIESEC全球有127個地方都有 而主要香港學生去多geh包括波蘭 巴西 羅馬尼亞 摩洛哥 泰國 越南 台灣等等<br />\n主要係6-8個禮拜義工 上面2750係programme fee會包住宿同每日最少一餐 機票保險其他使費就自費 可以試下申請學校subsidy<br />\nInterview depends on你間大學有冇first in 但generally你報咗個project之後對方個project manager都會同你skype傾下了解下你 但輕鬆geh<br />\n仲有冇咩想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31de4b389ac94470abfbbf598a2359cf61b539f","tid":270603,"uid":7731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打都係經aiesec?</blockquote><br />\nyesss</blockquote><br />\n聽日開始我都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過係Serbia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHey AIESEC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b7523fc842bd65e061d5adb255a944f2990ea9","tid":270603,"uid":90296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:54:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打都係經aiesec?</blockquote><br />\nyesss</blockquote><br />\n聽日開始我都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過係Serbia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我program聽日開始<br />\n你去serbia做咩？教英文？</blockquote><br />\n教中文啊，你program係摩洛哥？幾時完啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfa6806586aac5866e845f19f6aa263bb363024","tid":270603,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>義工program 洗唔洗比錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n經機構報<br />\n畀$2750 $1000可以拎返<br />\n包六星期食宿</blockquote><br />\n邊間想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2069897836c4ea8850eeb801444f03046313f92b","tid":270603,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>義工program 洗唔洗比錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n經機構報<br />\n畀$2750 $1000可以拎返<br />\n包六星期食宿</blockquote><br />\n邊間想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇到了 自膠"},{"pid":"b93ec553042110eea1d0463c7e219425a47696f8","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打都係經aiesec?</blockquote><br />\nyesss</blockquote><br />\n聽日開始我都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過係Serbia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我program聽日開始<br />\n你去serbia做咩？教英文？</blockquote><br />\n教中文啊，你program係摩洛哥？幾時完啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n7月17<br />\n有機會既話一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da26843c43d1351f439032e72f72486e16fe6d9f","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打都係經aiesec?</blockquote><br />\nyesss</blockquote><br />\n聽日開始我都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過係Serbia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我program聽日開始<br />\n你去serbia做咩？教英文？</blockquote><br />\n教中文啊，你program係摩洛哥？幾時完啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw 我讀中文都唔敢教中文"},{"pid":"62b825209be45a4e75363fcc126ad7afc5940188","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:31:53.000Z","msg":"btw Aiesecer應該可以起到我底了<br />\n得我一個黎摩洛哥"},{"pid":"522b49f04c1337558e2f93ac30f6b1af97b2e440","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:37:26.000Z","msg":"晚餐，機構提供既：<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/043339_5eb8f5790aa06d46d1b17afbf524d0f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F043339_5eb8f5790aa06d46d1b17afbf524d0f1.jpg&h=7c24cceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日遇到隻貓，隻腳斷左，好痴人<br />\n（但佢身上好多螞蟻，hi到我成身都係蟻）<br />\n但我身上一蚊摩洛哥錢都冇，本身想罐魚畀佢食<br />\n岩岩終於等到食飯時間，拎左隻雞蛋出去搵佢<br />\n但搵極都搵唔到<br />\n最後有個女人抱住個細路女問我拎野食，我就畀左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/043430_d842985f1b2592facb11b874bd331cc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F043430_d842985f1b2592facb11b874bd331cc3.jpg&h=20d902c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eae0a52a837f0f9ae4b30f0045a3da17af65e86f","tid":270603,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:43:51.000Z","msg":"easter 個陣都去咗半個月, 但我同您相反方向, marrakech玩返上去再過spain<br />\n不過完全玩唔夠侯, 下次去要瘋狂行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw chefchaouen真係無心目中咁靚, 仲要有唔少中國遊客 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5731c0d374cef87adce9ff882ba5f3a6da0c8b88","tid":270603,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:46:40.000Z","msg":"同埋摩洛哥啲人真係好極端<br />\n有啲好nice 嘅人<br />\n又有好撚多真係好pk嘅人<br />\n去過一次之後, 決定以後再去, 只會行山同去沙漠玩, 因為整體來講真心啲人唔係幾好客"},{"pid":"7c1757fe02f5582952a2f4526d7b9e74e64cda36","tid":270603,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T21:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>easter 個陣都去咗半個月, 但我同您相反方向, marrakech玩返上去再過spain<br />\n不過完全玩唔夠侯, 下次去要瘋狂行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw chefchaouen真係無心目中咁靚, 仲要有唔少中國遊客 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行山唔多啱多<br />\nbtw 佢地可能好少見到asian <br />\n佢地由頭打量到我落尾<br />\n啱啱夜晚出街都會著返條長褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}